~/Notes\~
Insomniac is the fourth studio album from the punk rock band Green Day. It was released in 1995 on October 10, through the Reprise Records label. Though it reached #2 in the U.S. and went double Platinum, Insomniac did not have the sales endurance of its predecessor, Dookie, largely due to its slightly darker lyrical tone and more abrasive sound.
